    "content": "Bitcoin uses *compact* difficulty in it's block body",
    "created_at": "2022-06-08T18:53:24.603000+00:00",
    "attachments": null
  },
  {
    "author": "alexssd7fp",
    "category": "general",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "Do `2^256 / (0x00000000ffff0000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000 / <difficulty from the block body>)` to calculate the PoW difficulty",
    "created_at": "2022-06-08T18:58:42.571000+00:00",
    "attachments": null
  },
  {
    "author": "alexssd7fp",
    "category": "general",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "```py\n>>> 2**256 // (0x00000000ffff0000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000 // 29900000000000)\n128421481706700456244754\n```",
    "created_at": "2022-06-08T18:59:21.433000+00:00",
    "attachments": null
  },
  {
    "author": "alexssd7fp",
    "category": "general",
    "parent": "",
    "content": "= 128.4 ZH",
    "created_at": "2022-06-08T18:59:32.037000+00:00",
    "attachments": null
  }
]